# =============================================================================
# NOTES
# =============================================================================

# This .gitignore file is configured for Terraform projects with IBM Cloud
# provider. It excludes sensitive files while preserving important project
# structure and documentation.
#
# Key exclusions:
# - Terraform state files (contain sensitive resource information)
# - Variable files (may contain API keys and secrets)
# - Temporary and backup files
# - IDE-specific files
# - Operating system artifacts
#
# Key inclusions:
# - Example and template files for documentation
# - README and documentation files
# - Script templates and examples
#
# Security considerations:
# - Never commit actual .tfvars files
# - Use .tfvars.example for documentation
# - Store sensitive data in environment variables or secure vaults
# - Review commits for accidentally included sensitive data
